<ab facs="#facs_291_r1l5">hat / daʒ Jr von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>cʒog</expan> Ernſten <expan>eẅ<ex>r</ex>m</expan> <expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſtanden</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_291_r1l6">habt / daʒ ſein gnade . <expan>ʒwıſche<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>derſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> vnd Bertleins von </ab>
