<ab facs="#facs_291_r1l18"><expan>ſecʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>beſchaıd<ex>en</ex></expan> / dahin wır <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>botſch<ex>aft</ex></expan> <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> . <expan>vngeu<ex>er</ex>lıchen</expan> </ab>
