</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_291" id="144v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Ernsten und <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Wilhelm<ex>m</ex></expan>, <expan>gebrud<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von
                        Peyern </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> von der von Swangöw
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> zu nehst
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und uns nu ewr
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Wilh<ex>e</ex>l<ex>m</ex></expan> gnade
                            <expan>geantw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan> hat, daz ir von
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Ernsten, <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan>
<expan>brud<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>v<ex>er</ex>standen</expan> habt, daz
                        sein gnade <expan>zwische<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ders<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> und Bertleins
                        von Swangöw, <expan>gebrud<ex>er</ex></expan>, und
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> ein gütlich ansteen beredt hab bis <app>
<note><q type="date">auf sand Jacobs tag schierist künftig</q>25.07.1421</note>
</app> etc., das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir wol
                                <expan>vernome<ex>n</ex></expan>. Nu hat uns ewr
                            <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan> Ernsts gnade vor
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>, daz die
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> von Swangow die sache von des
                        Zesels <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> gen uns in gut
                            <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan> ansteen <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>,
                        bis <app>
<note><q type="date">auf sand Jacobs tag schierist</q>25.07.1421</note>
</app>. Also wie wol wir mit den <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> von
                        Swangöw niht <expan>and<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>zu schike<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> denn guts, so <expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        wir doch <expan>dass<ex>elb</ex></expan> gütlich ansteen gen in auch also
                                <expan>halte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lichen</expan> und <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> mit fleiss, ob wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> darynn niht <expan>geniesse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möchte<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz uns die
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> von Swangow von des Zesels
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> on sprüch
                            <expan>lasse<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>wölte<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz uns denn ewr
                            <expan>furstenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> gnade <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>gerawme<ex>n</ex></expan> tag für ewr
                            <expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan>
<expan>secze<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>beschaid<ex>en</ex></expan>, dahin
                        wir <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>welle<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lichen</expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> glimpf
                        vor <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>fürstenl<ex>ichen</ex></expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>en</ex></expan> zu erczeln, daz wir
                            <expan>hoffe<ex>n</ex></expan> bey gelimpf zu besteen. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>hoch<ex>wirdikeit</ex></expan> dienst und wolgefallen etc. Und
                                <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> des ewr gnedig
                                <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<expan>antw<ex>ur</ex>t</expan>
<expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> bey disem <expan>bott<ex>en</ex></expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
